328
00:18:50,031 --> 00:18:54,751
[Yueyang Sect]

329
00:19:08,431 --> 00:19:10,991
[Mount Changming Sword Immortal, Ye Bai Yi]

330
00:19:12,631 --> 00:19:17,231
I, Chief of the Five Lakes Alliance, Gao Chong,
