333
00:19:28,271 --> 00:19:29,351
You brat.

334
00:19:29,951 --> 00:19:31,511
How dare you?

335
00:19:32,431 --> 00:19:34,511
Big Brother is here to welcome
Mount Changming Sword Immortal.

336
00:19:34,991 --> 00:19:36,951
