374
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:47,960
Men of the Sword Immortal are indeed
unfathomable.

375
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,120
Sister Xiang.

376
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:02,560
You are...

377
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:03,960
