00:23:55,928 --> 00:23:57,808
[Gao Xiao Lian is his only daughter.]

425
00:23:59,048 --> 00:24:01,608
[No matter what's his reason of
befriending Cheng Ling,]

426
00:24:01,888 --> 00:24:03,728
